<ul>
	<li>A <b>spot</b> is a rectangle that holds an individual car</li>
	<li>A <b>space</b> consists of 2 spots, side by side</li>
	<li>Cars move from space to space, ignoring any other cars</li>
	<li>If the end space is blocked with cars in both spots, put car in first space with a free spot <i>behind</i> the cars that blocked you</li>
	<li>Movement = Speed + Slipstream</li>
</ul>


<h3>Step Details</h3>

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
			<h4>4. Adrenaline</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Only applies to last car <i>to move</i> (last 2 for 5+ players)</li>
				<li>May add 1 speed, before or after boost (boost not required)</li>
				<li>Gain access to 1 extra cooldown</li>
				<li>May gain cooldown, while waiving +1 speed</li>
				<li>Can use both advantages during <b>5. React</b></li>
			</ul>
			
			<h4>5. React</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Activate symbols in any order (e.g. cooldown, boost)</li>
				<li>Symbols come from cards played, adrenaline or current gear</li>
			</ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
			<h4>6. Slipstream</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Optional</li>
				<li>Available if landing next to another car, or in a space behind a car</li>
				<li>Move 2 spaces forward, max 1<span class="cross"></span> per turn</li>
				<li>Does <b>not</b> increase speed</li>
				<li>Cannot slipstream across the finish line, or after crossing</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h4>7. Check Corner</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Only applies if crossing a <b>corner line</b></li>
				<li>If <b>speed</b> exceeds limit by X, pay X heat</li>
			</ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
			<h4>
				<img src="~/lib/Images/Heat/boost.png" />
				Boost
			</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>May boost once per turn to increase speed</li>
				<li>Pay 1 heat <span class="arrow"></span> reveal cards until speed card</li>
				<li>Works just like stress card</li>
			</ul>

			<h4>
				<img src="~/lib/Images/Heat/speed.png" />
				Speed
			</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Cards played (speed and stress)</li>
				<li>Boost</li>
				<li>Adrenaline</li>
			</ul>

			<p>Slipstream does <b>not</b> add speed, only movement</p>

			<h4>
				<img src="~/lib/Images/Heat/cooldown.png" />
				Cooldown
			</h4>
			<p>For each cooldown symbol, may move 1 heat card from hand to engine</p>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
			<h4>Spin Out</h4>
			<p style="margin-top: 0;">Not enough heat for excess speed</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Pay all available heat</li>
				<li>Move back to first available space before the corner</li>
				<li>Take 1 stress card into hand, take another if in 3<sup>rd</sup> or 4<sup>th</sup> gear</li>
				<li>Move to 1<sup>st</sup> gear</li>
			</ol>

			<h4>Cluttered Hand</h4>
			<p style="margin-top: 0;">Unable to play enough cards because too much heat</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Use all available cards, cover the difference by <i>playing</i> heat cards</li>
				<li>Car does not move this turn</li>
				<li>Move to 1st gear</li>
				<li>Cards in play area go to discard pile</li>
				<li>Skip directly to step 9</li>
			</ul>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

